"name": "12V to 5V LT1086-5 Regulator Block",
"description": "Reusable fixed 5 V linear regulator block based on LT1086-5. The block accepts an external VIN supply and provides a regulated VOUT. It includes the recommended input and output capacitors. The fixed 5 V version uses pin 1 as ground/reference.",
